I really want to talk to this one guy. I don't know him very well but he intrigues me. Say it aint so your drug is a heart breaker. Say it aint so my love is a life taker. So, I find this one guy who I am totally falling for but at the same time there's another boy. Here's a good example of how I kind of feel, this morning I saw a hummingbird skipping from flower to flower tasting all the flavors instead of just staying at one sucking all of the flavor till there's none left. I find it hard to concentrate on one boy I don't know why. I like to meet all different types of guys not just stay with one for a long time. I don't know what to do? I don't want to go out with this one guy yet because what if this other guy is good for me too? What do I do? I can't tell him that I like other guys or he'll be sad and that's the last thing I want for him. I need to make a decision...But, why? I think i'm going to have some fun with this for awhile... haha. Shhh...Don't tell anyone.
